I can close windows one by one without worrying abut SEGFAULTing. I also checked that `gtk_application_get_windows (app) == NULL` is only true after the last window is closed, using this diff:
```
diff -u /usr/src/debug/app-editors/gedit-3.28.1/gedit-3.28.1/gedit/gedit-commands-file.c /var/tmp/portage/app-editors/gedit-3.28.1/work/gedit-3.28.1/gedit/gedit-commands-file.c
